logistics_prompts.prompt: I want to order coffee $3.50 per pound for 500 lbs of coffee from the Tatooine farm
logistics_prompts.description: Initiates group chat coordination between Farm, Shipper, Accountant, and Helpdesk (optional) agents. Broadcasts order request (500 lbs @ $3.50/lb) and tracks multi-agent collaboration through order fulfillment workflow.
